txt.en: 'While the wood is now solid, there is much yet to do before we can put archers on the tower and have it ready to defend the village. While banners may sound trifling, they send a message to the Enemy that we have returned and will stand strong against anything they have to throw against us. There is also much to do to allow for the archers to man the tower itself.'
'Hytbold is one step closer to being rebuilt and restored.'
Tower of the Sutcrofts: Enhancements III
